  "description": "WHO WE ARE 🔺\n\nWe go by the name NOT RED — a visual identity that disrupts, provokes, and embodies tension. In our world, red, black, and white aren’t just colors — they’re emotions and states of mind.\n\nEvery frame becomes a visual hallucination, perfectly synced to sound.\n\nBut we don’t just make visuals — we build sensory environments meant to shift perception and stretch experience. Whether live, in motion, or lingering long after, NOT RED isn’t something you just watch.\nIt’s something you feel. And it leaves an imprint.\n\n#touchdesigner #dj #producer #audiovisual [ touchdesigner, audiovisual, techno, hypnotic, repetition, visual art, live, di, producer, phaserbeats, notred ]",
